{"tid":2250483,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"兩次遊青島 (日本四國)","createTime":"2020-10-20T06:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:31:30.000Z","uid":372770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae1fd1cd8f3386719f5fb5411369dd1ec5f135f","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"早幾年喺舊登睇到有巴去青島撚貓撚得咁過癮<br />\n我又跟足佢個行程過去治癒一吓<br />\n<br />\n香港下午上機<br />\n夜晚到大阪<br />\n梅田轉通宵巴士去松山<br />\n<br />\n去到松山凌晨5點幾 由於叔叔不行鳥<br />\n所以去酒店瞓先 (反正預左幾日 咁去唔到都抵輸)<br />\n<br />\n估唔到咁順利第一次去就有船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PwZCjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PwZCjq.jpg&h=9d7a298a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住落嚟會係咁出相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKgfaHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKgfaHw.jpg&h=7de77328&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba7b1073ee8ae7cee86653b4e0ee079a39930f0","tid":2250483,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89735f6bca82bac8f15b9823b713a1394666c5ef","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"嗰朝天氣麻麻 落住毛毛雨 好彩又唔算好凍 (聖誕前去 松山落住雪)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sydho78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSydho78.jpg&h=ce62b6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcWCo79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcWCo79.jpg&h=ce39f4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXcaJ8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXcaJ8a.jpg&h=967ba7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHpcXtc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHpcXtc.jpg&h=3b7ca6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdW61UT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdW61UT.jpg&h=59247bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭啲貓係無視本人 然後我做咗件仆街事<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n我伸手入袋整啲聲出嚟 成堆貓雙眼發哂光以為有飯開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgzPZHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgzPZHQ.jpg&h=b0ed716e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有隻仲抓住我隻腳想爬上身摷我個袋<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVMnAgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVMnAgF.jpg&h=cd10e3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而事實上我除咗帶咗幾隻蕉 蛋糕同水<br />\n係冇拎其他嘢餵佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5720b73862e556757d336d7e1ee8f36a0e34891","tid":2250483,"uid":175208,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"89735f6bca82bac8f15b9823b713a1394666c5ef","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"嗰朝天氣麻麻 落住毛毛雨 好彩又唔算好凍 (聖誕前去 松山落住雪)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sydho78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSydho78.jpg&h=ce62b6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VcWCo79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVcWCo79.jpg&h=ce39f4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXcaJ8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXcaJ8a.jpg&h=967ba7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHpcXtc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHpcXtc.jpg&h=3b7ca6c4&s={SIZE}\" />