cx/i/Znh2AKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnh2AKh.jpg&h=247ed151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能啲貓淋濕身覺得凍啦<br />\n就爬上我身取暖<br />\n開頭兩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znqLyws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FznqLyws.jpg&h=460fdb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzDtwh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzDtwh8.jpg&h=9e03db7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住變四隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8cYTw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8cYTw1.jpg&h=4ec15e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後再多三隻上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就再坐喺度變咗瞓喺度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBuAbje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBuAbje.jpg&h=99b395dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔夠位 連我個袋都唔放過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/265GRjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F265GRjH.jpg&h=45b7cf5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5bb85e2486e689d89fc04a5f186253b5c5a75a4","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"做咗人肉暖墊粒幾鐘 停咗雨 仲出太陽<br />\n落返去周圍行 影吓景又影吓貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfMGcCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfMGcCv.jpg&h=26c0ecfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kz41cCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKz41cCy.jpg&h=4b8ff1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtvf1vR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvtvf1vR.jpg&h=5dc385b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lpcx3Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpcx3Ke.jpg&h=d823a9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAvWLXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAvWLXA.jpg&h=5f79ae9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9pgLXV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9pgLXV.jpg&h=6d955023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksqr8bg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fksqr8bg.jpg&h=5b5bf4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位頸帶小朋友勁得意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y435EiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY435EiL.jpg&h=d7c828af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kA98B5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkA98B5r.jpg&h=fdf52a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又拖多兩隻上身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8ZAg5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8ZAg5S.jpg&h=610ecd58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVYJqZh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVYJqZh.jpg&h=34cad09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後屋主見到我坐咗喺佢屋企外面<br />\n就叫我出返去碼頭 聽語氣就唔似鬧掛........"},{"pid":"9773bd5eca2a5070703755ea9bff44948fa4dea1","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"又唔知坐咗幾耐 忽然啲貓走哂過碼頭嗰邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtRSkAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtRSkAB.jpg&h=e2d9a21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來下午船嚟咗 離開倒數1小時<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9Kkuud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9Kkuud.jpg&h=74107c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟咗兩個日本人 佢地比我好 有帶嘢食嚟餵佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BWKV9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BWKV9v.jpg&h=5f9b0043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdewA9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdewA9w.jpg&h=203eee3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開完飯聚哂喺上船位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDtJshC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDtJshC.jpg&h=083ab104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGEMp4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGEMp4i.jpg&h=2e5554f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好自律 最多去到甲板 唔會上船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySYM9wq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySYM9wq.jpg&h=791701f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠鐘開船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yp4pbKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYp4pbKW.jpg&h=592c1041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCKAipX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCKAipX.jpg&h=7c28c541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過咗幾年 見佢twitter話已經將所有貓絕哂育<br />\n加上島民越嚟越少 所以舊年趁未變荒島之前 去埋最後一次"},{"pid":"d556a95b3cf4e89c2e136c0f5fe7816154659b06","tid":2250483,"uid":372770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"第二次去 事前plan嗰陣有諗過伊予長浜附近可能有民宿<br />\n朕check完 是有的<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.oozukankou.jp/yado-n.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oozukankou.jp%2Fyado-n.html&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYET11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=83196c9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.oozukankou.jp/yado-n.html</a><br />\n不過一間得電話 另一間send咗email但係冇回覆<br />\n<br />\n算<br />\n住返松山<br />\n<br />\n呢次預咗5日 但係最終拎咗兩日出嚟搭通宵巴來回東京參加女優簽名會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一日去 欠航 即時搭下一班車返松山瞓覺<br />\n第二日又欠航 跟住搭咗去八幡浜鳩行 當晚搭通宵巴過東京<br />\n如是者去到最後一日 不成功 便下次再去(或者唔再去)<br />\n<br />\n好彩最後一日有船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kwmfqty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwmfqty.jpg&h=95ffc541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d07934ab3637049eb825954eaebee7c118eb91a","tid":2250483,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"d貓唔知去左邊，唔見左好多"},{"pid":"7b342121096b63b1bfc405665a538ae7b50be7d7","tid":2250483,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"I'm considering getting a temporary job in The Four Seasons in Japan because I'm interested in working there temporarily.  It'll improve my vocabulary and I'm sure it'll be an extraordinary experience. The air conditioning in The Four Seasons is sometimes set too low. My friend Susanna who's a vegetarian loves to eat coconuts and shea butter in Honolulu and Malaysia. She lives in Cochrane Street while her cousin's husband lives in Clovelly Court. They're gonna print off the score of Tchaikovsky sonata for tuba teaching."}]}